source: Allow to configure the JSON API in Open Social.

Consumers can access the API. The main goal is that the developer of a consumer application will create the consumer. That consumer will provide the configuration necessary for that particular application.

Documentation for the API is available for sitemanagers.
This module enables a JSON API for your Open Social site.
